Detailed Description

Struct to hold info about the file format for dataset.

Description:

Holds information pertinent to file IO for a dataset.

NOTE: only the members of this strut should have dynamic data because it's easier to do cleanup here (via _fc_closeDataset). The infos for sequeces meshes, subsets and variables should NOT have dynamic data.

Modifications:

  • 7/14/2005 WSD created.
